WEBVTT

00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:02.590
We then also have what we call general tools,

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:07.750
which are more for general business process and managing workflows,

00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:11.110
and they can be everything from automated testing through to grabbing builds,

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:14.230
reporting crashes. So for some more specific examples,

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:16.350
to tools that you may be familiar with because

00:00:16.360 --> 00:00:18.630
they've been seen on around the verse previously,

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:22.350
is Copy Build, which is used by pretty much every developer every

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:26.990
day to pull builds from the build system that is housed in Austin.

